title: Curve Men Cologne Spray, 4.2-Ounce
description: Curve For Men is freshly masculine. It is a cool, sensuous scent that is also edgy and complex. Green leaf and Douglas fir combine with cactus, amber, and wood to create an exhilarating freshness. The packaging is innovative: bottles are packaged in metallic tins in muted colors of citrine and amber.

title: Lacoste Essential By Lacoste Eau De Toilette Spray 4.2 Oz For Men
description: Lacoste Essential By Lacoste Eau De Toilette Spray 4.2 Oz For Men : Lacoste Essential was introduced in 2005 by Lacoste as a citrus, fruity scent for men. The masculine scent possesses a blend of tomato leaves, citrus, fruit and watery for the top notes. The middle notes include black pepper and florals. Finishing off with patchouli and sandalwood.
